{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "94c4bf85-7619-4d42-b8b3-786c0c66819b", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/94c4bf85-7619-4d42-b8b3-786c0c66819b@1.pkg/1772597509205/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597510235", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/94c4bf85-7619-4d42-b8b3-786c0c66819b@1.pkg/1772597509205/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597510235"}, "identifier": "94c4bf85-7619-4d42-b8b3-786c0c66819b", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>本题考查监察机关的职责。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>监察委员会对职务违法和犯罪进行调查，案例中监察委员会完成调查，故③符合题意监察委员会将案件移送检察机关属于处置职责，故④符合题意。惩办职责属于司法机关，监察委员会无此职责，故说法错误。检察职责属于人民检察院，故②说法错误。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>（原创）2025年4月，山西省人大常委会环境与资源保护工作委员会原主任薛某（正厅级）涉嫌受贿一案，经山西省监察委员会深入调查终结，正式移送检察机关审查起诉。在这一案例中，监察委员会行使的职责是（ &nbsp; &nbsp; ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①惩办职责 &nbsp; &nbsp;②检察职责 &nbsp; &nbsp; ③调查职责 &nbsp; &nbsp;④处置职责</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（原创）2025年4月，山西省人大常委会环境与资源保护工作委员会原主任薛某（正厅级）涉嫌受贿一案，经山西省监察委员会深入调查终结，正式移送检察机关审查起诉。在这一案例中，监察委员会行使的职责是（     ）①惩办职责    ②检察职责     ③调查职责    ④处置职责", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-nd